79
00:04:11,417 --> 00:04:15,501
If it's just a GIF, can I click on a profile or a link?

80
00:04:15,501 --> 00:04:17,504
Where is that info, right?

81
00:04:17,504 --> 00:04:20,327
So that's findability is the next step.

82
00:04:22,225 --> 00:04:22,705
Accessibility.

