87
00:04:35,356 --> 00:04:38,178
to make an informed decision as to whether I like your game

88
00:04:38,178 --> 00:04:40,220
and most importantly, whether I'm gonna buy it

89
00:04:40,220 --> 00:04:41,241
or support it.

90
00:04:41,241 --> 00:04:45,244
