00:04:51,071 --> 00:04:53,074
Have you done it within their attention span?

95
00:04:53,074 --> 00:04:54,236
That's really big.

96
00:04:54,236 --> 00:04:57,160
And is the information you've given them clear

97
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,822
and representative of the experience,

98
00:04:58,822 --> 00:05:01,406
or at least the experience you want them to have?

99
00:05:02,327 --> 00:05:04,748
I know that it's a little harder pre-launch

