00:07:23,494 --> 00:07:26,496
This is an assumption that a lot of us make

145
00:07:26,496 --> 00:07:29,979
when we work on super, super small teams.

146
00:07:33,061 --> 00:07:37,943
I think it's, I have a lot of sympathy for this one because I think that talking about

147
00:07:37,943 --> 00:07:42,625
this kind of stuff takes up an immense amount of mental space.

148
00:07:42,625 --> 00:07:46,306
