199
00:10:07,209 --> 00:10:10,211
why your game is different from every other game

200
00:10:10,211 --> 00:10:13,212
that uses the term you're using, such as roguelike?

201
00:10:13,212 --> 00:10:16,033
Or are you just alienating an entire audience off the bat?

202
00:10:16,033 --> 00:10:19,855
When you're pitching to, say, a narrative studio,

203
00:10:20,355 --> 00:10:23,459
please use all the narrative shorthand you want, right?

