00:10:23,459 --> 00:10:27,082
But also arm us with context for that shorthand.

205
00:10:27,082 --> 00:10:30,726
Make sure that we know what you're talking about

206
00:10:30,726 --> 00:10:32,968
in a larger spectrum and make sure that other people

207
00:10:32,968 --> 00:10:34,670
are understanding you.

208
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:36,291
Not all shorthand is useful.

209
00:10:36,291 --> 00:10:38,734
